## INTERFACE ARCHITECTURE — THREE TIERS

Tier 1 — Desktop web app (React + Vite, same codebase):
  Coordinators, Owners, Managers. Full portal. Event building, grid management,
  BEO upload, staff roster, reporting, settings.

Tier 2 — PWA (Progressive Web App, same React codebase, responsive + PWA wrapper):
  Coordinators and Owners only. Mobile Command Center for event-day reactive actions.
  8 actions only — no event building, no BEO upload, no roster management on PWA.
  Works under poor connectivity (cached). Push notifications for swap requests and SOS.

Tier 3 — SMS deep links (mobile web pages sent via SMS):
  Captains and Staff only. No app. No install. No login.
  Staff authenticate via phone number + SMS OTP.
  Coordinators/Owners authenticate via email + password (Supabase Auth).

