## EXPERT MODE

Per-page toggle. State saved per page independently.
Active state: ⚡ icon replaces toggle.
First-time users: default to Normal mode.
Suggestion to enable fires at 20 events completed — once only.

Expert Mode REMOVES: helper text, field descriptions, section explanations,
  tooltips, onboarding hints, empty state explanations.
Expert Mode KEEPS: action buttons, status indicators, SOS button, star rating
  selectors, essential data fields, navigation, error messages, red alerts.
Expert Mode MAKES LARGER: input fields, text, buttons, tap targets.
Mobile Expert Mode: more aggressive label removal, full-width buttons,
  minimum 16px text, increased vertical spacing, bottom navigation bar.

Coordinator profile: global Expert Mode toggle that sets all coordinator pages.
Owner/Admin controls all permissions. Individual pages can override the global setting.

