## RATING SYSTEM

Staff ratings: 1–4 stars. Never 5 stars. Never a slider. Never a text input.
The RatingStarSelector component is a 4-tap UI. Tap = set, hold = submit.
Minimum 1 star. No zero rating option. Confirm tap required before submitting.
Ratings are INTERNAL. Staff never see their own rating.
Star count on staff cards: coordinator/captain view only.

Rating floor on grid rows: set via same 4-star tap UI.
Event-level floor set at top of Build Grid — all slots inherit.
Position-level override available but must not lower below event floor silently.
Safety check: if more than 30% of slots on a Wedding or Gala are set to 1-star,
  system flags this before saving.

