## SCHEDULING RULES

One staff member = one slot per event day. Hard block at database level.
Exception: 3-hour gap between shifts allows two assignments same day.
All 3-hour gap overrides are logged with: approver, timestamp, amber ⚠ badge.
Never silently override a scheduling conflict. Always surface it to the coordinator.

