## AUTOMATED ACTIONS — REQUIRE COORDINATOR APPROVAL

These actions NEVER publish automatically without coordinator review:
  - AI grid suggestions
  - Schedule disruptions affecting confirmed staff
  - Channel resets (GridMaster Connect)
  - Follow-up SMS at 48-hour postponement window

Option B (flag and prompt) is the standard pattern for automated changes.
The coordinator sees the proposed change and must approve before it fires.

