## SOS CENTER

SOS Urgent: medical, fire, major venue failure, safety threat.
  → All management immediately. Escalates at 5 and 10 minutes if no response.
Alert — Needs Attention: missing supplies, staffing gap, venue access.
  → Coordinator + backup. Escalates at 15 minutes.
Update — FYI: minor issue. Coordinator only. No escalation.

Person who triggers SOS is the ONLY person who can mark it resolved.
SOS is always internal — client never knows.
Staff do not have an SOS button. Pre-event personal emergencies via SMS keyword SOS only.

