## MOBILE COMMAND CENTER (PWA — CATERING)

8 actions and nothing else. This is not an event-building screen.

1. All-events status strip (green/amber/red dot + captain check-in + health check dot)
2. Call-out → instant backfill (one tap triggers rated replacement search)
3. Staff transfer (moves staff between events; both grids update; captain notified via SMS)
4. Emergency fill — single position (filter by role and rating floor)
5. Unexpected temp approval (approve or flag; captain notified instantly)
6. Shift swap approval (both events side by side; approve or deny; both captains notified)
7. Late arrival logging (expected time; captain auto-notified; grid updated)
8. Quick staff contact (tap to call or SMS any staff member across active events)

Rating floor on transfer: when coordinator transfers a higher-rated staff member,
  system shows the minimum rating tier needed to fill the vacated slot.

