## CAPTAIN HEALTH CHECK SMS

Fires 2 hours before event start time.
Reply options: 1 = All good | 2 = Waiting | 3 = Need help.
Health check dot is separate from and smaller than the main event status dot.
  Green = replied 1 | Amber = no reply in 20 min OR replied 2 | Red = replied 3.
No-reply at 20 minutes: amber dot, no push notification to coordinator.
1-hour check: skipped if captain replied 1 at 2-hour mark.
  Fires if captain replied 2, 3, or did not respond.

